{"tid":850530,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【食得唔好嘥】型男大廚走入街市執剩菜 如何$0煮四餸一湯？","createTime":"2018-10-06T14:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T08:01:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"555da96ebfdef5d02fb336a1d2a0493356780977","tid":850530,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:32:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_58667789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw.nextdigital.com.hk%2Farticle%2F3_58667789&d=zvjwJMnJdsybTlaoe9kqo9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=bcb733fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_58667789</a><br />\n<br />\n【食得唔好嘥】型男大廚走入街市執剩菜 如何$0煮四餸一湯？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 1006 00:01<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181005/large/1538729851_da08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F1538729851_da08.jpg&h=0aaadd46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181005/large/1538729843_30ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F1538729843_30ee.jpg&h=064c4e84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181005/large/1538729842_fba6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F1538729842_fba6.jpg&h=e997153b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181005/large/1538729846_c9ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F1538729846_c9ed.jpg&h=53620be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181005/large/1538729845_0ce3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F1538729845_0ce3.jpg&h=fe213052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181005/large/1538729845_7cb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F1538729845_7cb8.jpg&h=ee11544e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181005/large/1538729851_5cfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F1538729851_5cfb.jpg&h=72c1d86d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181005/large/1538729852_50b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F1538729852_50b3.jpg&h=59482bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n  <br />\n【食得唔好嘥】型男大廚走入街市執剩菜 如何$0煮四餸一湯？（足本版）： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2O4fhSi \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2O4fhSi%20&d=zvjwJMnJdsybTlaoe9kqo9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=065e9dc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2O4fhSi </a><br />\n<br />\n電視都有廣告提醒我們別做大嘥鬼，要珍惜食物，減少浪費。其實街市每天都有不少被人棄置的食材，它們沒有腐壞，只因為賣相不漂亮或不夠新鮮，賣不去惟有棄掉。<br />\n<br />\n其實這些廚餘只要好好利用，隨時一毫子也不用，也可以煮到美味的食物來。「我不嬲都唔鍾意嘥嘢食，尤其是啲菜瘀咗，我都煮嚟食。」名廚Justin說。今日他便帶我們去他平日逛的街市，看看有甚麼好東西可以執回去做菜。<br />\n<br />\n這個位於中環結志街的街市，出名多高級餐廳來入貨，難怪不要的東西都優質過人。Justin今天很幸運，先後在菜檔、海鮮檔及凍肉店都執到廚餘。結果他只用了一些家常做法，便煮了四菜一湯，包括麻辣涼拌大豆芽、韓式燒牛小排、鹹蝦醬炒通菜、炒香葉蛋飯及芫荽番茄鯽魚湯。不只賣相吸引，味道也好。最重要的是，惜食的意義重大，尊重每一個食材，像Justin一樣尊重每一個食材，吃得便不要浪費。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：黎詠詩<br />\n攝影：梁偉德、王瑋彤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關文章：<br />\n【西營盤消夜美食｜型廚Justin帶路食鑊氣小炒 椒鹽白飯魚勁香口】：<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/LXfpzi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FLXfpzi&d=zvjwJMnJdsybTlaoe9kqo9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=57d437b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/LXfpzi</a> <br />\n<br />\n【有獸醫唔讀揸鑊鏟 型廚有個開通阿媽：媽咪係我老友口】：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2OAdrrX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OAdrrX&d=zvjwJMnJdsybTlaoe9kqo9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=48542584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2OAdrrX</a>  <br />\n<br />\n更多 飲食男女 文章"},{"pid":"1d462ac7718f821dbcb5ab194d722b2c312edb3e","tid":850530,"uid":121130,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:34:52.000Z","msg":"左二對波好似好大"},{"pid":"ce38a2da0fbc8551f2b9768bc82f802bb0e3167c","tid":850530,"uid":94828,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:35:12.000Z","msg":"啲女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 左邊人妖咁款<br />\n連右邊啲鬼妹都咁柒"},{"pid":"97ca8595892d049f15f97ef2c04488a6af8406d3","tid":850530,"uid":86125,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33fc66950146c42291ca20ec4e5dd49b44ae42f1","tid":850530,"uid":45007,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T14:36:10.000Z","msg":"肉點會廚餘到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f142145abb6e2cf14e551ca97f5bc8963041e4","tid":850530,"uid":134549,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:00:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8463ff0ec555ad4d9c268460d173d15f57b9452","tid":850530,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1fabfadb8ca38abc0d0397c12d13e0f8a050dae","tid":850530,"uid":56661,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:28:44.000Z","msg":"左一<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TotBC5T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%